OL,3,CLancashire rider dies during Pre-TT
OL,4,Cclassic road race on the Isle of Man
OL,6,FA rider from Lancashire has died
OL,7,Fduring an incident at the Pre-TT
OL,8,FClassic Road Races.
OL,10,FAlan Oversby, 68, from Bolton-Le-
OL,11,FSands, lost his life during the 400cc
OL,12,Frace on Sunday 24 May, in an event
OL,13,Fpreluding the world-famous Isle of Man
OL,14,FTT.
OL,16,FThe accident occurred on the approach
OL,17,Fto Ballakeighan, on the second lap of
OL,18,Fthe race.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
