OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1779719232
OL,3,CLancashire rider dies during Pre-TT
OL,4,Cclassic road race on the Isle of Man
OL,6,FOrganisers described Mr Oversby as an
OL,7,F'experienced competitor', first
OL,8,Fcompeting in 2005 and taking his first
OL,9,Fvictory in 2006.
OL,11,FHe has since taken 16 wins at the
OL,12,Fevent, including two today.
OL,14,FSouthern 100 Road Races wished to
OL,15,Fextend their 'deepest sympathy to
OL,16,FAlan's wife Julie, family, team and
OL,17,Ffriends'.
